## Voice Direction Notes
- **Emphasis**: Hook, value props, CTAs, surprising facts
- **Pauses**: Minimal - only for dramatic effect or transition
- **Inflection**: Enthusiastic, varied, authentic
- **Energy**: Consistent high energy, peak at hook and CTA

## Platform-Specific Guidelines

### TikTok / Instagram Reels (15-30s)
- **Hook**: First 1-2 seconds critical
- **Pacing**: 165-180 WPM
- **Style**: Trend-aware, relatable
- **CTA**: Follow, save, share

### YouTube Shorts (30-60s)
- **Hook**: First 3 seconds
- **Pacing**: 160-175 WPM
- **Style**: Value-forward, retention-focused
- **CTA**: Subscribe, comment, next video tease

### LinkedIn Video (30-45s)
- **Hook**: Professional but engaging
- **Pacing**: 155-170 WPM
- **Style**: Value-driven, credible
- **CTA**: Connect, visit website, download resource

